            <bioghist>
                <p>Hannah Bacon Evans (1839-1939) was the daughter of Thomas Evans (1798-1868) and
                    Catharine Wistar (c. 1801-1871).</p>
            </bioghist>

            <scopecontent>
                <p>This is a collection of approximately 150 letters from Hannah Bacon Evans written
                    between 1888 and 1923, primarily to Edith Silver, but also to other family
                    members. The letters mainly focus on Evans's family life and visits from
                    friends, but in some letters she refers to current events. The collection also
                    includes seven disks containing transcriptions of the letters.</p>
            </scopecontent>

